                <p><img class="noBorder floatLeft paddingRight" alt="Heaven Facial" src="http://www.heavenskincare.com/Images/Trade/facial.jpg" align="left" /> Heaven Health &amp; Beauty Ltd has many assets: scientific skills and varied high level techniques, conscientiousness and exceptional efficiency, constant concern for perfection, creativity and desire to innovate fostered by many international interactions, exceptional press coverage and a strong brand presence within the market place.</p>

